
Overview of noun motif

The noun motif has 3 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (5) motif, motive -- (a design or figure that consists of recurring shapes or colors, as in architecture or decoration)
2. (1) motif, motive -- (a theme that is repeated or elaborated in a piece of music)
3. (1) theme, motif -- (a unifying idea that is a recurrent element in literary or artistic work; "it was the usual `boy gets girl' theme")
